  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Longitudinal investigation of cognitive, emotional and illness awareness of schizophrenia
      outpatients (Shalvata Mental Health Center). The study uses computerized assessment of
      cognitive functioning and questionnaire to assess performance of patients assessed in the
      past as part of a routine clinical assessment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
